categories: Category:Events during the High Republic Era

nodes.text: During the High Republic Era, the Nihil attacked Tiikae. A Jedi starship travelling in the area, containing Jedi Master Cohmac Vitus, Jedi Knight Vernestra Rwoh and their Padawans, Reath Silas and Imri Cantaros, diverted to assist in repelling the attack. Rwoh had a Force vision of the attack while the starship was in hyperspace before she learned of what was going on, in which she saw an unusual object in the city under attack.
